title: Bee Gees - Best Of Volume 1 & 2 & Greatest
description:
Bee Gees - Best Of Volume 1 & 2 & Greatest

Best Of Bee Gees [Volume 1] (1969) has songs from 1967 to 1969.
Best Of Bee Gees Volume 2   (1973) has songs from 1968 to 1972.
Greatest (discs 1&2)        (1979) has songs from 1975 to 1979.

If you don't want all the songs in this torrent, 
I suggest those marked with an asterisk (*) after the track number.
